# Firmis Demo — VHS tape file
# Records `firmis init` running against a project with findings

Output .github/demo.gif
Output .github/demo.webm

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.5

Type "firmis init"
Enter
Sleep 8s
Type "n"
Enter
Sleep 5s
